name: The Rise and Fall
description:
The Rise and Fall, 2011

Giclee print on Hahnemuhle German Etching paper

Limited edition of 25

71.1 x 59.4cm. 
(mounted: 89.9 x 76.1cm.)


FREE postage & packing to the U.K.

NOTES:
1. The prints are made using the best archival paper and are backed with mounting card, behind a white window mount.
2. The prints are sold unframed, however framing can be arranged at extra cost. Please contact mail@hesterfinch.com for more info.
3. Please allow 2 weeks for delivery.
4. The prints will be sent first class with Royal Mail Recorded Delivery and will need to be signed for.
5. If you are purchasing from abroad, please contact mail@hesterfinch.com before buying to arrange shipping.
5. If a buyer is for any reason unhappy with their purchase, they may return the artwork in its original condition within 7 days of delivery at their own cost. They will be refunded the full amount, less shipping.
